title: Digital Dreaming FULL MOVIE HD Psilocybin Mushroom / Acid Trip
description:
Digital Dreaming FULL MOVIE
as seen on youtube 

If you wish to experience this movie full i suggest taking 1.5 to 2gm of dried Psilocybin Mushrooms on a nearly empty stomach 45min before you start the film, headphones a must and try not to be distracted with any other external stimuli.  Enjoy

This is a compilation of different clips i have been collecting over the years and put together over 6months to emulate what my massive dose of mushrooms was like (17gm dried). 
this is to try to show the ups, downs and just lost space of thought I experienced.
I find watching this move invokes some awesome thought prepossesses as well without any hallucinogens.
i have tried to convey the emotions the run with the experience but it is impossible for me to do, it's like trying to describe blue to a blind person, they can only be experienced. The absolute love, forgiveness, connection to everything and having epiphany after epiphany was mind blowing and sometimes quite scary as you face the truths of yourself
